From 3c5e054f07eb7f1a431a6c29766873a12aee5436 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Marios Trivyzas <matriv@gmail.com>
Date: Tue, 24 Jun 2025 17:03:45 +0300
Subject: [PATCH] Fix `c.r.allocation.awareness.*` settings to be visible in
 `sys.cluster`

Mark the 2 settings were as exposed, and implement allow the implicit
cast of `Settings` (because the `force` one is a group setting), to an
Object, so that it can be transparently used in `SysClusterTableInfo`.

Fixes: #18047
